rows.label: qst202511_0010
rows.name: Hmm. They seem to be having fun.

rows.label: qst202511_0020
rows.name: Yeah...

rows.label: qst202511_0030
rows.name:
Looking at them now, they almost
seem like a great team.

rows.label: qst202511_0040
rows.name: No...it's not this one either...

rows.label: qst202511_0050
rows.name:
Oh, where is it...?!
I was so sure I'd find it here...

rows.label: qst202511_0060
rows.name: Astelle, are you looking for something?

rows.label: qst202511_0070
rows.name:
Huh?
Ah...erm...

rows.label: qst202511_0080
rows.name:
If you tell me what your objective is,
I can scan the surrounding area for it.

rows.label: qst202511_0090
rows.name:
This will markedly increase
the likelihood of success.

rows.label: qst202511_0100
rows.name:
I'm sure that's true,
but I need to keep this secret.

rows.label: qst202511_0110
rows.name: I promise to tell you afterwards, though!

rows.label: qst202511_0120
rows.name: Understood.

rows.label: qst202511_0130
rows.name: Ah! There it is!

rows.label: qst202511_0140
rows.name:
KOS-MOS RE: Re:!
Look! Look!

rows.label: qst202511_0150
rows.name: Beware!

rows.label: qst202511_0160
rows.name: Astelle! Leg it!

rows.label: qst202511_0170
rows.name: Gyaaa!

rows.label: qst202511_0180
rows.name: KOS-MOS RE: Re:?

rows.label: qst202511_0190
rows.name: Are you unhurt?

rows.label: qst202511_0200
rows.name:
Hey, you need to be a bit more careful, KOS-MOS RE: Re:!
What if you'd have hurt yourself?

rows.label: qst202511_0210
rows.name:
It's OK.
Please do not worry about me.

rows.label: qst202511_0220
rows.name:
And, more urgently, please conceal
yourself behind me for a moment.

rows.label: qst202511_0230
rows.name: I will take care of this swiftly.

rows.label: qst202511_0240
rows.name:
You'd better not get hurt, KOS-MOS RE: Re:!
But you'd better not lose, either!

rows.label: qst202511_0250
rows.name:
Incompatible orders received.
But, orders acknowledged.

rows.label: qst202511_0260
rows.name:
Adjusting priority order of prime directives.
Prioritizing orders from Astelle.
